A helmet is a piece of equipment that protects player's head. There are many helmets in RuneScape. A helmet may refer to:

  • Metal helmets:
    • Medium helmets
    • Full helmets
  • Barrows helmets:
    • Dharok's helm
    • Verac's helm
    • Guthan's helm
    • Torag's helm
  • Special helmets:
    • Fremennik helmets
    • Khazard helmet
    • Crab helmet
    • Gilded full helm
    • Initiate sallet
    • Proselyte sallet
    • Granite helmet
    • Tyras helmet
    • 3rd age full helmet
    • Rock-shell helm
    • Helm of neitiznot
    • Slayer helmet
    • Serpentine helm
      • Magma helm
      • Tanzanite helm
  • The head slot
  • Items worn in the head slot:
    • List of all items worn in the head slot.
    • Table of all items worn in the head slot.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
